# PGP Automation Framework

## Project Context
Enterprise-grade test automation framework for Paytm's Payment Gateway Platform (PGP) built with Java 11, TestNG, Selenium, and RestAssured.

## Framework Architecture

### Base Test Class Structure
```java
public class YourTestClass extends PGPBaseTest {
    // Page objects — declare as fields
    private final CheckoutPage checkoutPage = new CheckoutPage();
    private final ResponsePage responsePage = new ResponsePage();
}
```

### CORRECT IMPORTS (always include exactly these for test classes):
```java
import com.paytm.api.GetPaymentStatus;
